platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 不思議な世界を探索しよう

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 幻想的な世界を旅しよう
瀕死戰士踏上征途 尋找救命解藥
深入失落荒地，尋找治癒重症秘方

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Pixel-perfect art brings a lost world to life in the gorgeous Hyper Light Drifter. Explore vivid forests, bright landscapes, and the shell of a high-tech society overgrown by nature as you seek to cure a fatal illness. Packing silky smooth, lightning-fast combat, Hyper Light Drifter is a blast—even when you’re just admiring the scenery.
